high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a spatula from the counter
Move to the sink to the left
Clean the spatula in the sink
Move to the counter to the right of the fridge
Put the spatula on the counter to the right of the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spatula to the counter to the right of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, head to the counter
Take the spatula from the counter
Turn to the left, head to the sink
Put the spatula in the sink, turn on the water
Turn off the water, take the spatula from the sink
Turn to the right, head to the microwave, put the spatula in front of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Wash the spatula, put it in front of the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and the left again to face the cabinet with the bread on it.
Pick the spatula up from the table.
Go left and turn to the right to face the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the spatula up.
Turn to the right and then the right again to face the microwave.
Put the spatula down on the table in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula down in front of a microwave.
